# Tilemap Studio statically links FLTK 1.4.5, built X11-only, because Ubuntu
# 26.04 ships FLTK 1.4.4 as a Wayland-hybrid build that upstream's X11 window
# code will not compile or run against. FLTK is built from a sha256-pinned
# upstream release in build.sh against the SYSTEM png/zlib/jpeg, so only FLTK
# itself is embedded; kept under review per FLTK release.
tilemap-studio: embedded-library [usr/bin/tilemapstudio: fltk]
